text:
Austrian ski resort Ischgl was one of the epicenters of #SARSCoV2:
- 1,473 tested (79% of population) in late April
- 42.4% have antibodies
- 6x higher than PCR tests
- 85% asymptomatic
- 9 hospitalizations, 2 deaths 
https://t.co/Ea731PrP7N
